RESORT STYLE CLUBHOUSE FEATURING QUALITY SHOWS LIKE GLORIA ESTEFAN, ARTS AND CRAFT CLASSES, CARD ROOM, PUTTING GREEN, OLYMPIC SIZE HEATED POOL WITH LAP POOL, JACUZZI, FITNESS CENTER, A CAFE/RESTAURANT, A BAR, BILLIARDS, SHUFFLEBOARD, TENNIS, PICKLE BALL, AND SO MUCH MORE!  RARELY AVAILABLE, THIS 4 BEDROOM, 3 BATHROOM WITH EN SUITE, IS VERY WELL MAINTAINED. FEATURING 12' CEILINGS, A NEWER KITCHEN WITH QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS AND COLOR CHANGING LED LIGHTS, ALL TILE FLOORS, RETRACTABLE CEILING FANS, CROWN MOULDING, AND GORGEOUS FIXTURES ON A NEUTRAL PALATE. WITH NEWER APPLIANCES AND WATER HEATER, YOU CAN'T MISS THIS GEM!!
